        "template--16192486834354__f2365400-d403-425a-a677-b3d1e19401f4-liquid-1": {
          "type": "liquid",
          "settings": {
            "code": "<h2>OUR STORY</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify\">Have you ever found yourself lost in the endless blue open waters, feeling the cool breeze gently touching your face and perfectly complementing the warmth of the summer sun?<br><br>\n\nHave you ever gazed at a perfect sunset over the water while letting your daily stress and worries give way to a true feeling of awe and appreciation?<br><br>\n\nIf you had, you may be one of us, looking for any opportunity to spend more time on the water. Be it sailing, fishing, or some adrenaline-filled Jet Ski fun.<br><br>\n\nWe are two friends from sunny Sarasota Florida, that share a passion for open waters and the freedom and excitement that comes from riding on a Boat or Jet Ski. <br><br>\n\nWe always loved tinkering with our ”water toys” and coming up with new ideas for making our boating experience safer and more enjoyable. One day, while brainstorming how to make a better beach anchor, we decided to share our ideas with the world and founded WavesRx.<br><br>\n\nSo if you’d love to join us on this journey, it would be a privilege to have you on-board!<br><br>\n\nRemember, boat is nothing without water and man without his dreams!</p>",
            "width": "50%",
            "alignment": "top-middle"
          }
        },
